                                                                                        富士通統合レポート2025<span class="c-link-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 60 60" aria-hidden="true"><path class="arrow" d="M26.3,41.9c-0.2,0-0.4-0.1-0.5-0.2c-0.3-0.3-0.3-0.8,0-1.1l10.9-10.9L25.7,18.8c-0.3-0.3-0.3-0.8,0-1.1 s0.8-0.3,1.1,0l11.4,11.4c0.3,0.3,0.3,0.8,0,1.1L26.8,41.7C26.6,41.8,26.5,41.9,26.3,41.9z"></path><circle class="circle" cx="30" cy="30" r="28"></circle></svg></span>
                                                                                    </a>
                                                                                </p>

                                                                        <div class="c-panel__text">富士通統合レポート2025を公開しました。お客様への提供価値の向上とネットポジティブの実現を目指す私たちの取り組みを様々な切り口でお伝えします。</div>
                                                                </div>
                                                                                                                                                                                </div>
                                                            <div class="c-panel__media">
                                                                <img src="/-/media/Project/Fujitsu/Fujitsu-HQ/about/integrated-report/2025/kv-integrated-report-2025-936x578.jpg?rev=bf0b73d64dc94d0f9d5d85b20f76d42a&amp;hash=3C9D0121FD2F5566AA0D24A391B6CE4B" alt="富士通の役員集合写真"
                                                                     width="860" height="532" loading="lazy" class="c-panel__media-item">
                                                            </div>
                                                    </div>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="c-collay_item ">
                                            <div class="c-panel">
                                                    <div class="c-panel__wrap">
                                                        <div class="c-panel__body">
                                                                <div class="c-panel__content">
                                                                                <p class="c-panel__title">
                                                                                    <a class="c-panel__title-text" href="/ja-jp/technology/research/quantum" target="_self" >
                                                                                        Fujitsu Quantum<span class="c-link-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 60 60" aria-hidden="true"><path class="arrow" d="M26.3,41.9c-0.2,0-0.4-0.1-0.5-0.2c-0.3-0.3-0.3-0.8,0-1.1l10.9-10.9L25.7,18.8c-0.3-0.3-0.3-0.8,0-1.1 s0.8-0.3,1.1,0l11.4,11.4c0.3,0.3,0.3,0.8,0,1.1L26.8,41.7C26.6,41.8,26.5,41.9,26.3,41.9z"></path><circle class="circle" cx="30" cy="30" r="28"></circle></svg></span>
                                                                                    </a>
                                                                                </p>

                                                                        <div class="c-panel__text">富士通は2030年、量子コンピュータでビジネスをリードします。本特設ページでは、富士通の量子コンピュータの技術をご紹介します。</div>
                                                                </div>
                                                                                                                                                                                </div>
                                                            <div class="c-panel__media">
                                                                <img src="/-/media/Project/Fujitsu/Fujitsu-HQ/technology/research/quantum/kv-quantum-936x578.png?rev=e524f76758f04efe8ac85f1069b96044&amp;hash=0F27EBE45B6D8A76B1430DF846F65871" alt="富士通の256量子ビット 超伝導量子コンピュータの写真"
                                                                     width="860" height="532" loading="lazy" class="c-panel__media-item">
                                                            </div>
                                                    </div>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="c-collay_item ">
                                            <div class="c-panel">
                                                    <div class="c-panel__wrap">
                                                        <div class="c-panel__body">
                                                                <div class="c-panel__content">
                                                                                <p class="c-panel__title">
                                                                                    <a class="c-panel__title-text" href="/ja-jp/local/blog/article/2026-03-24-01" target="_self" >
                                                                                        異業種の“非常識”が、問いを強くする──共創の場「FUJI HACK」から見る新規事業創出のヒント<span class="c-link-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 60 60" aria-hidden="true"><path class="arrow" d="M26.3,41.9c-0.2,0-0.4-0.1-0.5-0.2c-0.3-0.3-0.3-0.8,0-1.1l10.9-10.9L25.7,18.8c-0.3-0.3-0.3-0.8,0-1.1 s0.8-0.3,1.1,0l11.4,11.4c0.3,0.3,0.3,0.8,0,1.1L26.8,41.7C26.6,41.8,26.5,41.9,26.3,41.9z"></path><circle class="circle" cx="30" cy="30" r="28"></circle></svg></span>
                                                                                    </a>
                                                                                </p>

                                                                        <div class="c-panel__text">異業種の“非常識”が問いを強くする。富士通の共創の場「FUJI HACK」は、多様な知見で常識を覆し、新規事業の種を探る実践の場。イノベーション創出のヒントを提供します。</div>
                                                                </div>
                                                                                                                                                                                </div>
